* tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man (Standards): Document it.

Prompted by a similar change to mandoc(1).
---
 tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man | 2 ++
 tmac/mdoc/doc-syms    | 2 ++
 3 files changed, 11 insertions(+)

diff --git a/tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man b/tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man
index b31358ad3..4eaaded23 100644
--- a/tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man
+++ b/tmac/groff_mdoc.7.man
@@ -2503,6 +2503,8 @@ Part 1: System API
 .St -p1003.1-2004
 .It Li \-p1003.1\-2008
 .St -p1003.1-2008
+.It Li \-p1003.1\-2024
+.St -p1003.1-2024
 .El
 .Pp
 .
diff --git a/tmac/mdoc/doc-syms b/tmac/mdoc/doc-syms
index 4db4373b3..c637fe242 100644
