 .as doc-str-St--p1003.1-2008   " (\*[Lq]\)\*[Px]\*[doc-str-St].1\*[Rq])
+.ds doc-str-St--p1003.1-2024   \%IEEE\*[doc-str-St] Std 1003.1-2024
+.as doc-str-St--p1003.1-2024   " (\*[Lq]\)\*[Px]\*[doc-str-St].1\*[Rq])
 .ec
 .
 .\" POSIX Part 2: Shell and Utilities
